column3: “Smoked a bowl of Suicide Girl this morning. Great for a wake and bake strain. I felt giggly and happy. Had coffee and ate breakfast and felt the need to get up and go for a nice walk. Felt great and lasted for a good few hours. Fantastic!”
“One of the only strains that doesn't leave me tired while burning out. All time fave!”
“Extremely relaxing to the mind body and soul”
